    "en": {
      "title": "Criminal gangster shot dead in shootout",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A Criminal Gangster was shot dead by police during a shootout in Yakkala.",
        "Police Spokesperson, Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Talduwa said that a T56 firearm was also found in the possession of the deceased suspect.",
        "According to reports, the gunned-down gangster was identified as Ihala Vithanage Joseph Kumara alias Elpitiye Joseph (41).",
        "It is reported that he was a close associate of Underworld Gangster Ganemulla Sanjeewa, and is suspected to have carried out the shooting at Bastian Mawatha, Colombo on 30th May 2022.",
        "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win"
      ],
